Title: Bayesian Discrete Random Graph with Covariate Dependent Partitions and Covariates
Description: The package allows for clustering Graphs with binary obesrvations in R.
  It provides a comprehensive set of functions and algorithms tailored specifically for the 
  challenges posed by discrete and heterogenius random graphs data.
